  "content": {
    "problemStatement": "### **Aptitude Practice Question**\n\nFind (121/10)x = 3.\n\n---\n\n### **Answer & Explanation**\n\n\u00a0Apply logarithm on both sides\nlog(121/10)(121/10)x = log(121/10)3\nx = (log 3) / (log 121 \u2013 log 10)\nx = (log 3) / (2 log 11 \u2013 1)",
    "sampleTestCases": []
  }
